title: 이달의소녀탐구 #414 (LOONA TV #414)
summary:
0:01 -- HyunJin practices her facial expressions and starts memeing.
0:28 -- It's 2:40AM and they are all ready to go home. YeoJin changed into casuals and is super excited. Olivia Hye in the back gives and awkward smile. "Are you really shooting me in casuals?" YeoJin barges in and stands in front of her.
0:46 -- It's so late and YeoJin is still energetic. She can't stop speaking to the camera. Hye shows her mis matched shoes.
